Package: friendlynumber
Title: Translate numbers into English numerals
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(
  "Ethan", "Sansom", 
  email = "ethan.sansom29@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre")
  )
Description: Converts number vectors to character vectors of numerals, including cardinals (one, two, three) and ordinals (first, second, third). Supports negative numbers, fractions, and arbitrary-precision integer and high-precision floating-point vectors provided by the {bignum} package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
URL: https://github.com/EthanSansom/friendlynumber
BugReports: https://github.com/EthanSansom/friendlynumber/issues
Suggests: 
    bignum,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
